text:
Welcome to the digital version of my poster presented at the APA 2024 Seattle Conference!
I am excited to share my research with you.
On this website, you will find:

The digital version of my poster
The list of references cited in my research
Information about me and my work

title: About
text:
I recently graduated with a Ph.D. in Social Work and am currently working as a Postdoctoral Fellow at New York University Steinhardt School of Culture, Education, and Human Development and the Arcadia Suicide Center.
My research focuses on the prevention of adolescent suicide attempts. I am passionate about data science and machine learning, continually seeking to apply these tools to improve outcomes in my field.
You can learn more about my work and publications by clicking the button below:
Visit My Website
